metadata.name: MønaLisa
metadata.description:
**Cyborgs**.

Blocks of flesh and ink designed over photos, videos and animations: unveiled through an analog-digital structure that I call WIRE.

A portal-entity between worlds that no longer collide, because they are now indistinguishable in wired NFTs.

\*
MønaLisa is a cyber painting that – through WIRE – exposes, subverts and frees the canonical artwork.
